Package: missBayes
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Differential Expression Analysis for Proteomics with Missing Data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Venk Mallikarjun, Mengchun Li
Maintainer: Mengchun Li <limengchun1122@gmail.com>
Description: Performs Bayesian differential expression analysis on proteomics data. 
    The core model explicitly accounts for missing values, by modeling the log fold change posterior distribution. 
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Imports: rjags, coda, parallel, matrixStats, limma, stats, methods
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
